channel.title: Opening doors on a PI
channel.description: Okay well this is probably a newby question but how can I open doors for my PI. I went to doors.cfg but there is only a handful of doors there and not the ones I need. Do I just add the door in or is there somewhere else I need to go like objecthandler.java? Its not a huge issue but would be nice to have the doors open.
